net.infonode.properties.base
Interface Property

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractProperty
public interface Property

A property is belongs to a PropertyGroup and contains name, description, type etc. A property can have multiple values which can be stored in any type of object.

Version:
$Revision: 1.1 $
